I hear you are a master of controlling\nmana and researching wyrmscale alike.\nIf true, I would request your aid.

I will get to the heart of the matter:\nI seek the mana-controlling device\nyou createdâ€”I seek the World Ark.

You would proffer up one of Levin's\nforbidden dragonseeds? Fascinating.
I had heard they had all been destroyed.
This is the last of the original three.\nBut if it will let me obtain what I seek,\nit is a price worth paying!

Thank you for your support. Ha ha ha!
Heh heh. I am glad to have you as\na test subject, my dear prince.
I look forward to seeing what a\ndistant relative of mine can do...
One day, rumors began to spread of a village in\nSouth Grastaea whose residents had vanished\nwithout a trace.
Soon, word came down of another village that\nhad suffered the same fate. ...And another.\n...And another still

I am investigating the possibility this may\nhave been the work of a legendary fiend\nthat absorbs people.

I assure you, I mean no harm.

researcher investigating the strange
